  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Immediate Start Sales Executive!!!!",
  "description": "<p>🎉 <strong>Sales Executive – Train With Us, Get Paid Weekly</strong></p><p>Looking for a job that actually teaches you something <em>and</em> pays on time (every week 👀)?<br />If you like talking to people, learning new skills, and earning based on effort — welcome aboard.</p><p>🗣️ What You’ll Be Doing</p><ul><li><p>Chat with customers and introduce products/services</p></li><li><p>Learn how to sell confidently (don’t worry — <strong>training is included</strong>)</p></li><li><p>Turn interest into sales and earn commissions 💰</p></li><li><p>Work with a fun, supportive team that’s got your back</p></li><li><p>Level up your communication and people skills</p></li></ul><p>📚 We Train You First</p><ul><li><p><strong>Full training provided from Day 1</strong></p></li><li><p>No experience needed — we teach you everything</p></li><li><p>Coaching, guidance, and support throughout</p></li></ul><p>💸 Why This Role Is Worth It</p><ul><li><p><strong>WEEKLY PAYOUT 💵</strong></p></li><li><p>Fast hiring & immediate start</p></li><li><p>Basic pay + commission + incentives</p></li><li><p>Great for students, fresh grads, or career switchers</p></li></ul><p>✨ Who Fits Right In</p><ul><li><p>Friendly, motivated, and willing to learn</p></li><li><p>Comfortable talking to people (or ready to improve)</p></li><li><p>Enjoys a fast-paced, energetic environment</p></li><li><p>Experience is a bonus, not a must</p></li></ul><p><strong>Learn fast & get paid weekly.</strong><br />Apply now — limited spots available 🚀</p>",
